msgid "Place this line in your wp-config.php file to secure the key."
msgstr "Sitúa esta línea en tu archivo wp-config.php para asegurar la clave."

#: includes/class-security.php:182
msgid "DFX Parish Retreat Letters: Encryption Key Mismatch"
msgstr "DFX Cartas de Retiros Parroquiales: Claves de cifrado no coinciden"

#: includes/class-security.php:185
msgid ""
"The encryption key defined in wp-config.php does not match the one stored in "
"the database."
msgstr ""
"La clave de cifrado definida en wp-config.php no coincide con la almacenada "
"en la base de datos."

#: includes/class-security.php:188
msgid "Warning:"
msgstr "Atención:"

#: includes/class-security.php:189
msgid ""
"Only the key defined in wp-config.php will be used. If any messages were "
"already encrypted using the database key, they will become unreadable."
msgstr ""
"Solo se empleará la clave definida en wp-config.php. Si ya existe algún "
"mensaje cifrado con la clave de la base de datos, se volverá ilegible."

#: includes/class-security.php:192
msgid "You can either:"
msgstr "Puedes:"

#: includes/class-security.php:195
msgid "Update the key in wp-config.php to match the database key, or"
msgstr ""
"Actualizar la clave en wp-config.php para que coincida con la clave de la "
"base de datos, o"

#: includes/class-security.php:196
msgid ""
"Remove the key from the database to use the wp-config.php key (click the "
"button below)"
msgstr ""
"Eliminar la clave de la base de datos para usar la definida en wp-config.php "
"(haciendo clic en el botón de debajo)"

#: includes/class-security.php:200
msgid "Remove Database Key and Use wp-config.php Key"
msgstr "Eliminar clave de base de datos y emplear clave de wp-config.php"

#: includes/class-security.php:215
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to remove the encryption key from the database? Any "
"messages encrypted with the old key will become unreadable. This action "
"cannot be undone."
msgstr ""
"¿Estás seguro de que deseas eliminar la clave de cifrado de la base de "
"datos? Cualquier mensaje cifrado con la clave antigua se volverá ilegible. "
"Esta acción no puede deshacerse."

#: includes/class-security.php:216
msgid "Removing..."
msgstr "Eliminando..."

#: includes/class-security.php:217
msgid "An error occurred. Please try again."
msgstr "Ha ocurrido un error. Inténtalo de nuevo."

